# Environment Variables Example
# OpenAI API key is configured server-side via Netlify environment variables.
# Set OPENAI_API_KEY in your Netlify site settings (Site > Configuration > Environment variables).

# Note: The app will work without OpenAI API key using Tesseract.js fallback
# For best OCR results, add your OpenAI API key from https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
